title: Genitourinary trauma.
summary: This article discusses identifying the significant injuries, those patients at risk for developing these injuries, and the radiographic procedures that will effectively stage these injuries so that appropriate management can be proposed....
abstract: Evaluation of genitourinary trauma can be confusing. This article discusses identifying the significant injuries, those patients at risk for developing these injuries, and the radiographic procedures that will effectively stage these injuries so that appropriate management can be proposed.
